# RXSS

## Simple feed reader web app

I've made this for myself and as a way to learn JS, it's designed to be used on mobile devices with Termux but works on PC. May be clunky but works as intended, I also *may* fix and add new features.

## Features
* Load X amount of articles (3 by default) and change the amount of articles of specific feeds.
* Save feeds locallly to access it offline.
* Read articles directly from the app, or go to the article's page.
* Change the feed's title color.

## Project Structure
### /public
- Holds the frontend
### /public/lib
- Third party libraries (jscolor & prism)
### /public/svg
- Radix Icons
### /userdata
- Holds the saved links, feeds and configuration